"{\"correct\": \"no\", \"explanation\": \"The code incorrectly uses sns.lmplot() within the g.map() function. The lmplot() function is a figure-level function and cannot be used in this context, which expects an axes-level function. Instead, sns.regplot() should be used for plotting within the FacetGrid.\", \"patch\": \"6c6,7\\n< g.map(sns.lmplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n---\\n> g.map(sns.regplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n> g.add_legend()\" }"